      <title>特朗普回归前，韩国预算之争考验尹富根</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/south-korea-budget-tussle-tests-yoon-ahead-of-trump-s-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈的领导能力面临又一次考验，因为主要反对党正在争夺年度预算控制权，而这一结果将进一步让人怀疑他在国家准备迎接唐纳德·特朗普回归之际制定政策的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/south-korea-budget-tussle-tests-yoon-ahead-of-trump-s-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 07:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>极右翼领导人誓言，除非出现“奇迹”，否则将推翻法国政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/far-right-chief-vows-to-sink-french-government-unless-miracle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国民联盟主席乔丹·巴德拉在法国预算辩论中强化了极右翼的立场，增加了政府最早在本周被推翻的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/far-right-chief-vows-to-sink-french-government-unless-miracle</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 07:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
